bacci.giovanni.bio.sequencing

Class FrequencyPullStreamer

  • java.lang.Object
    • bacci.giovanni.bio.sequencing.SequencePullStreamerDecorator
      • bacci.giovanni.bio.sequencing.FrequencyPullStreamer
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    SequencePullStreamer, Iterable<Collection<FilePointerContainer>>

    public class FrequencyPullStreamer
extends SequencePullStreamerDecorator
implements Iterable<Collection<FilePointerContainer>>
    Object that store each sequence in a frequency table using a FilePointerContainer for each file. This class can be used with these SequenceStreamer:
    RandomFastaSequenceStreamer
    This class convert each sequence passed through the pull(String, Object...) method into an hashCode. If you are planning to pass more than 2^32 unique sequences this class may generate "String collision".
    Author:
    Giovanni Bacci
